Snoo Says Yes (FKA Better Reddit Check) - a Chrome extension

Receive instant visual feedback whether any URL has been submitted to Reddit.
If the page you're on has been submitted, you can open a new tab to join 
the discussion, or you can resubmit the link. Otherwise, you can start 
a new submission right from the Chrome toolbar.

Snoo Says Yes is maintained by paulburton0 [at] gmail.com and is 
distributed under the GNU General Public License - see the accompanying 
LICENSE file for more details.
 
Extension install link:
https://chrome.google.com/extensions/detail/bnikifloagjncfjbniboapgdehnlemmd

Source available at:
